#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:38
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; is a program for learning touch typing. It helps you learn to "
"type on a keyboard quickly and correctly. Every finger has it's place on the "
"keyboard with associated keys to press."
msgstr ""
"&ktouch; ni A Porogaramu ya:  Kwandika :$1 . Kuri Ubwoko: ku A Mwandikisho "
"na . ku i Mwandikisho Na: Utubuto Kuri Kanda . "

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:41
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-ktouch; helps you learn to touch type by providing you with text to "
"train on, and adjusts to different levels depending on how good you are. It "
"can display which key to press next, and correct finger to use."
msgstr ""
"&ktouch; Kuri Ubwoko: ku Na: Umwandiko Kuri ku , na Kuri Intera ku . "
"Kugaragaza: Urufunguzo Kuri Kanda Ibikurikira > , na Kuri Koresha . "

#. Tag: para
#: man-ktouch.1.docbook:44
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "This application is part of the official &kde; education module."
msgstr "Porogaramu ni Inzira %s Bya i &kde; Modire . "

